@startuml
[*] --> EnteredDetails : user entered details
EnteredDetails --> Registered : system requires citizens to register before logging in
Registered --> LoggedIn : system allows citizens to log in if their login details are correct
LoggedIn --> UploadDocuments : system enables citizens to upload documents, view their profile, or apply for a certificate after logging in
UploadDocuments --> ContinueUploading : system allows citizens to continue uploading documents if needed after initial uploads
ContinueUploading --> ApplyForCertificate : system enables citizens to apply for multiple certificates and reapply after sending a request to the issuer
ApplyForCertificate --> RequestedCertificate : system allows registrars to request certificates for verification
RequestedCertificate --> ContinueRequesting : system enables registrars to request multiple certificates and continue requesting more after receiving one
ContinueRequesting --> SessionEnded : system ends the session once the user is done with their actions
@enduml
